        "created_at": "2016-08-16T06:28:50.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I guess the short answer is yes\u2014though they will also naturally remain quite vibrant, acid-driven wines. I\u2019ve been revisiting a few 2014s in the last few weeks, and they\u2019re developing beautifully, but slowly. This stuff seems really built for the cellar, which is quite refreshing.</p>",
